  "title": "Freelance Bengali Interpreter needed",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><p>A premier litigation process service firm which provides services like translation, transcription, interpretation and staff outsourcing company.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are seeking a skilled Bengali transcriber/translator based in Singapore for a short-term project under one month. You will deliver precise transcription and translation services between Bengali and English, supporting legal proceedings with expert verification.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Transcribe audio recordings from Bengali to English and English to Bengali with accurate timestamping to ensure precise legal documentation</li><li>Translate documents and audio content between Bengali and English with high accuracy to maintain original meaning and context</li><li>Verify and certify the authenticity of your transcription and translation work by signing affidavits for court submission</li><li>Serve as an expert witness in court hearings to clarify and defend the accuracy of your translations and transcriptions when required</li><li>Apply advanced listening skills to capture clear and complete audio content for transcription and translation purposes</li><li>Manage your workload independently, delivering high-quality outputs within agreed deadlines to support timely legal processes</li><li>Provide detailed proposals including relevant experience and links to past projects demonstrating expertise in Bangladeshi transcription and translation</li></ul>",
